MG_WarmCup_Headshot

When the round starts, after 5 seconds everyone gets a weapon and get teleported to a stage to play in.
The weapon and map is each round RANDOM!

Whenever you get shot your HP will get back too 100!
so wanna kill someone you need to give a headshot.
(It is possible to get killed without headshot since alot of people could shoot you, and take hell of alot damage.

8 different stages to play in.
16 different weapons.


Map can be played in the WarmCup Community Mini-Game server 91.216.197.4:27044
